<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201006/626349b0c3c2478985d6db6bb1e4fdcd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201006/9562515e5d0c468c98e9178055984237.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>精选新鲜的柠檬</strong>，洗干净后切成一片片，柠檬<strong>清香</strong>扑鼻而来，忍不住想要先尝一口！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201006/7e28826917bf4fff8a26a05a0debfc89.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201006/91266c11baee45e1b0bde176c0578ef1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">将柠檬片放入<strong>雪克杯</strong>中，人手捶打出它<strong>新鲜的汁与肉</strong>！再加上<strong>冰与茶</strong>，充分<strong>摇晃</strong>，让他们味道更好得混合！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201006/40632f8eb3694c3fb198355510db0006.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">将他们倒入杯内，再加上<strong>脆啵啵</strong>，一杯<strong>真材实料</strong>的柠檬茶完成了！快来尝一尝吧～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201006/a4da243ca1ed467e8eb07437daaf0545.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 1/精神柠檬红茶• </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201006/37994a17b4e4411294d67a6aee11c011.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>柠檬配红茶</strong>，<strong>经典搭配</strong>但又<strong>让人上瘾</strong>。再加上冰块，吸上一口让你立刻<strong>精神</strong>起来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 2 / 一口茉柠香 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201006/27a7a5cb9ce947948896097436950c2a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>清清茶香味的茉莉</strong>与<strong>酸酸甜甜的柠檬</strong>混合起来，一口下来，让人<strong>心情舒畅</strong>～</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 3 / 茉柠脆啵啵•</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201006/aeebb62eee9a4fe9b6096d03f9fe0c8d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在<strong>茉柠</strong>上再加上<strong>Q弹的脆啵啵</strong>，一边喝一边嚼，<strong>既能吃又能喝</strong>，赞！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>• 4 / 卜卜脆柠檬红 •</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201006/72c99c1dd35b47c2a11b7bc4246de794.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Q弹的脆啵啵</strong>，咬开一口<strong>糖甜</strong>，在混合上<strong>柠檬红茶</strong>，绝配！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201006/072b3ce658a04185afa62b886acf01e7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">// 清新简洁的店面//</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201006/08bd615630cf45a5b6f246d3c63bfc96.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">店门便透出<strong>调皮的气息</strong>～玻璃店门上面贴上了<strong>店内功能</strong>，让人忍不住<strong>推开门进去瞧一瞧</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201006/5392398a8d754f9aa0bef2c670a4de4b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>纯色</strong>的墙面挂上一个个<strong>铁架子</strong>，中间放上<strong>绿油油的假植</strong>，架子上面贴满了<strong>五彩的食物造型灯</strong>，不妨顺便<strong>尝尝实物</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>木色的桌面</strong>，<strong>舒适的椅子</strong>，<strong>宽敞的过道</strong>，营造出一个<strong>舒适</strong>的环境，让人忍不住和闺蜜一起拍一张<strong>靓照</strong>记录记录！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201006/30b91afaa1084975bb340e122b4d4b48.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在店里等待你的到来噢～</p>
